info.description:
Cisco IOS-XE Native Configuration - System (Part 2)

Extracted from Cisco-IOS-XE-native YANG module.
**Category:** System (Part 2)
**Paths:** 182

**HTTP Methods:**

- PUT: Replace configuration
- PATCH: Merge/update configuration
